element.name: Views of Howth by kazidrat, Traditional Cache (1/3)
element.description: A short climb with great views.
element.long-description:
Cache is located on the wilder part of Howth, near the summit.
You can park your car at N 53. 22. 874 and W 006. 04. 669.
From the car park follow the path to the right of the hotel and continue up the hill.
The cache is a small container with logbook, pencil, some goodies and a new not yet registered travel bug = FTF price.
NOTE: The location might become very slippery in the winter or in wet weather. Kids should be supervised at all times.
